OL,4,G1345FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&Bers descend on Gateshead
OL,6,     Gfor the week's second visit, at
OL,7,     GSutherlands Hotel, where two
OL,8,     Gguests want revenge and are
OL,9,     Gdetermined to dig up some dirt.
OL,10,G1415FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GVisit three is to Hugh and
OL,12,     GLoretta's Brampton Dales Farm in
OL,13,     GLincolnshire. After an afternoon
OL,14,     Gout at an old jail, the B&Bers
OL,15,     Gfeel sheepish about an uninvited
OL,16,     Gguest at breakfast.
